/-- Loewner-majorant definiteness from packet endpoints.
    Data: (m11, r11, m22, r22, m12, r12, sh1, sh2) with
    sh1 = e11+e22-s, sh2 = 2*e12-s, s = min(e11+e22, 2*e12).  Claims:
